1 unit(s) Canned tuna
7 g Chives
1 tbsp Red Wine Vinegar
56 g Baby Spinach
56 g Carrot, julienned
113 g Baby Heirloom Tomatoes
1 unit(s) Shallot
2 tbsp Oil*
0.06 tsp Pepper*
¼ tsp Sugar*
0.13 tsp Salt*

Halve tomatoes.
Thinly slice chives.
Peel, then cut shallot into 1/4-inch rounds.

Add vinegar, chives, 2 tbsp oil and 1/4 tsp sugar to a small bowl.
Season with salt and pepper, then whisk to combine.

Add spinach, tuna, tomatoes, carrots and shallots to a medium bowl.
Drizzle dressing over top. Season with salt and pepper, to taste, then toss to combine.